  <brief_title>Evaluation of Different Continuous Positive Airway Pressure (CPAP) Systems in Patients With Acute Respiratory Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>The CPAP in Patients Affected by Acute Respiratory Failure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
